          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A Bayesian DWBA analysis was employed in order to",
                "extract C2S values while accounting for optical model",
                "uncertainties. The differential cross section of each",
                "state was fit simultaneously with the elastic",
                "scattering data in order to infer an overall",
                "normalization. An additional statistical uncertainty",
                "was also estimated separately for the elastic",
                "scattering and transfer data to account for",
                "deficiencies in the reaction theory. Cross sections",
                " (mb/sr) can be derived from the measured yields from",
                "the inferred normalization factor of 0.075 with a 9%",
                "systematic uncertainty. The elastic scattering data",
                "had an additional 15% statistical uncertainty. The",
                "additional uncertainty for the transfer cross",
                "sections varied from state to state, but can be taken",
                "to be 15% as an overly conservative average."
              ]
            }
          ],
